 en heftig leseropplevelse. Slutten kan selvsagt ikke r\u00f8pes."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|bok"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|bok|bokanmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6a39264432494514ca0f422e29ff0367ba3ecf91e083fee81f25ac07f655a36a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T17:25:24.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Global/lokal ungdom i hyllest til klassiske science fiction-filmer."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1271753.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/a%20bok_johan_harstad"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/853d09cddeb63a69ad4e89e4cdec88969fe0fdac.jpg?59862aac"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Velskrevet m\u00e5negr\u00f8ss -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "853d09cddeb63a69ad4e89e4cdec88969fe0fdac"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Literature"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Literature"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["bokanmeldelser", "kultur", "bok"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "boka"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["twin peaks og solaris", "mia", "twin peaks", "paris og tokyo", "aldrin og albert \u00e5berg", "alien", "antoine og midori"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["stavanger", "harstad"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "albert \u00e5berg"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/bok", "kultur", "kultur/bok/bokanmeldelser"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1271753.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/a%20bok_johan_harstad"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "V